    public ResponseEntity<ConvertedDatatablesData<MainWorkCenter>> HierarchyWorkCentersItemMainWorkCentersThymeleafController.datatablesByIdsIn(@RequestParam("ids") List<Long> ids, DatatablesColumns datatablesColumns, GlobalSearch search, DatatablesPageable pageable, @RequestParam("draw") Integer draw) {
        
        Page<MainWorkCenter> mainWorkCenters = getMainWorkCenterService().findAllByIdsIn(ids, search, pageable);
        long totalMainWorkCentersCount = mainWorkCenters.getTotalElements();
        ConvertedDatatablesData<MainWorkCenter> data =  new ConvertedDatatablesData<MainWorkCenter>(mainWorkCenters, totalMainWorkCentersCount, draw, getConversionService(), datatablesColumns);
        return ResponseEntity.ok(data);
